msg":"#metoo #麗瑤 #bitch #slut #老屈"},{"pid":"4ad520b4dbe6d607ee008c86560a08f10d461013","tid":929162,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"#believewoman  #believesurvivors #believevictims<br />\n「你唔駛對號入座！總之邊個做過，你自己心知肚明。我話係就係！唔使證據，呢度唔係法庭，唔需要證據，我對眼就係證據！哼！我睇人睇咗幾廿年，邊個係人邊個係鬼我睇得出，你立過咩心腸，做過咩事，你最清楚。」"},{"pid":"4f98cb9d3a078c8b5ee22c392c9fdf8a52580175","tid":929162,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c4abaffd000fad2a74d8e03f5e31d90166a44ca","tid":929162,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"三十年咁耐實告唔入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"就算告唔入, 都可以令你身敗名裂<br />\n<br />\n之前facebook 先成班人講:「就算法官判你無罪, 都唔代表你無做過, 只係證據不足」"},{"pid":"23fb9641e15b77c2e193a02576d15439afc1018f","tid":929162,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c721a1cda5a6de9bd5cd863cef6c93aad334b372","tid":929162,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.stsaa.org/web/wp-content/uploads/photo-gallery/%E4%B8%83%E5%8D%81%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4/14024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stsaa.org%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fphoto-gallery%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F14024.jpg&h=007b4a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張cap出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8acac80ccc9ffa7f1a6658d79fc09d9379ac7e9f","tid":929162,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f98cb9d3a078c8b5ee22c392c9fdf8a52580175","tid":929162,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c4abaffd000fad2a74d8e03f5e31d90166a44ca","tid":929162,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:36:14.000Z